latestIgtvVideos.title: Quick 4 step Skin care routine
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I am obsessed with skin care and can spend so much time on taking care of my skin but my reality as a mom is that Im rushing 99.9 % of the time so I need to find fast and effective ways to still get some me time in during the day. 
So I thought I share with you my 4 step skin care routine using products I’ve received from @goodmolecules 🖤 •
Products used:
1. Clarify and cleanse bar 
2. Niacinamide brightening toner 
3. Niacinamide serum 
4. Silicone free priming moisturizer.
My favorite thing about this brand is the simple ingredients, so I know exactly what I am using on my skin. *** please ignore the ugly cut on my chin and chipped nails  lol this is real life struggle, and I just wanted to create! Lolol

latestIgtvVideos.title: *10 min quick mommy makeup look *
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys ! So I asked you girlies what you would like to see and one of the requested videos was an everyday / mommy makeup look. I know how super busy we can get as women and as moms so I’m sharing with you my quick and easy look for the days you want to look cute . •
Products used: 
Eyebrows - NYX brow mascara color esperesso ( eyebrows are microbladed with @withaflourishnyc ) 
Concealer: @maybelline instant age rewind  eraser dark circles light pale 
Foundation: @toofaced peach perfect shade light beige 
Contour palette : @wetnwildbeauty megaglo 750 A caramel toffee 
Highlighting palette: @wetnwildbeauty illuminating palette 320 Catwalk pink 
Blush : @Elfcosmetics modern metals 
Setting spray : @tartecosmetics rainforest of the sea (used it of camera but it’s my go to ) •
Thanks for watching 😘😍😍😍
** if you want me to do another makeup look let me know ❤️ #everydaymakeup #mommymakeup #discoverunder2k #makeuplooks #makeuplover #selftaught #10minmakeup
